For both DOOM and Wine you can set the size of the window using the vdesk setting, in the style \(aqvdesk=600x300\(aq. \(aqfullscreen\(aq also works for doom and msdos apps.
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

.PP
Sommelier looks for the variables \(aqSOMMELIER_CA_BUNDLE\(aq, \(aqCURL_CA_BUNDLE\(aq and \(aqSSL_VERIFY_FILE\(aq, in that order, to discover the path of the Certificate Bundle for certificate verification. If \(aqSOMMELIER_INSTALLER_CACHE\(aq is set, sommelier will download installer and .zip files to the specified directory, and leave them there for future use with the \(aq-url\(aq option.
.SH APPS FILES

.PP
Installable apps are specified using \(aqapps files\(aq. These are files that contain one-line configurations for each app that can be installed. Each line starts with an application name, followed by a list of name-value pairs that specify configuration variables. The only required variable is \(aqplatform\(aq which specifies the platform for the app, e.g. "linux32", "winxp", "zxspectrum", etc. \(aqurl\(aq is also usually provided, which specifies the url that the app package can be downloaded from, however this can be ommitted if the url is provided at install time using the 
.na

.BR \-url
.fi
.ft P

.ad n
.nop command-line option (as in gog.com apps).
.PP
There are some special types of line that can be put in the file. Instead of starting with an application name, they start with a single symbol. These symbols are:
.nf
.ft CW
.RS
.EX

#    a comment line
!    a line of variables that apply to everything below it in the file
*    a line of variables that apply to everything below it in the file UNTIL another \(aq*\(aq line is encountered
.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  
.PP
For example, here is a file the configures a few 3ds homebrew games. Note how \(aqplatform\(aq and \(aqcategory\(aq are set using a \(aq*\(aq line to prevent typing them over and over for each app.
.nf
.ft CW
.RS
.EX

* platform=3ds category=Game;3DS

Breakout url=https://github.com/Magicrafter13/Breakout/releases/download/B_1.07.02/Breakout.3dsx install\-type=\(aqexecutable\(aq sha256=\(aq84c052828e6eac1d78831df9f4cac9eb8d5e580c766e567ed3e029ee75b77ac6\(aq category=BreakoutGame;3DS
ColossalCaveAdventure url=https://github.com/nop90/Colossal\-Cave\-Adventure\-2.5\-for\-3ds/releases/download/v1.1/Advent_3DSX_v1.1.zip sha256=\(aq57de0c3df074b0afdb1da75f43bc85d99fc07a65b13fea809a4a4bf3f3d13a6c\(aq category=DungeonCrawl;3DS
GriffonLegend url=https://github.com/nop90/Griffon\-Legend\-3DS/releases/download/v1.0/GriffonLegend.v1.0.zip sha256=\(aqbe29b374dcd722715fe24bae835174abb446e136ac306a5507dda92b5661c24f\(aq
.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  
.PP
