.SH REMOTE STORES

.PP
sommelier supports \(aqremote stores\(aq, directories containing app list files that can be downloaded from an http, https or ssh server. These are registered using:
.nf
.ft CW
.RS
.EX

	sommelier addstore <url>
.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  
.PP
where the url points to an apps list file. App packages can be stored in the same directory as the apps list file, and their urls can be specified using a variable called \(aqserver_path\(aq which specifies the directory part of the URL the apps list file was installed from. 
.PP
Installed apps files can be re-downloaded and updated using
.nf
.ft CW
.RS
.EX

	sommelier refresh
.RE
.EE
.fi
.in
.ad b
.nop  